- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper leverages the strength of deep learning to learn an aesthetics measure for 3D shapes autonomously, which falls under the scope of machine learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an aesthetics measure for 3D shapes, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence that deals with human perception and preferences.
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the applications of the proposed aesthetics measure in aesthetics-based visualization and search, which are relevant to multimedia systems.
